Subject: Re: [T2] Electronic ignition

It depends on if it's a California Model with Factory Hall Ignition or a
Federal 49 state model with Points.  If it's a Federal, the Pertronix and
AccuFire should install right in.  Not sure if Pertronix makes a
retrofittable ignition for the Hall Distributor that's compatible.

California Models
http://www.oldvolkshome.com/ignition.htm#V8083CA

Federal Models
http://www.oldvolkshome.com/ignition.htm#V8083FD
